# Skill Reasoning: last_change Convention

When editing a skill and adding/removing a causality hash (#for-X or #not-X) in the Reasoning section:

1. Update `reasoning_checksum` (run `node is/scripts/architecture/update-reasoning-checksums.js` or preflight).
2. Set `last_change: "#for-X — краткий контекст"` in frontmatter (replace X with the actual hash, add short context).

**Frontmatter order:** `id` always first; canonical order: id, title, tags, status, reasoning_*, last_change (SSOT: is/contracts/skill-frontmatter-order.js).

**Reference:** id:sk-d7bf67 (process-reasoning-audit).
